<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usupa26.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Supa26</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>1/9/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>12:30:01 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I figured it out</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Well, me and a friend spent yesterday giving each others tells on how we were going to figure this out... <br>
He has the legs and i have the robe, but legs have a long castign time (like 15 seconds) so he was experimenting in PoG while i was in Kael. <br>
FACT   /sit on and /sit off work...<br>
you can also use ctrl s to sit and stand (i was frustrated looking through the key settings and i noticed this one<br>
FACT you can't hit a hotkey whil you are casting it right? Well we figured out a way you can.<br>
<br>
First make the robe hotkey and put it in slot 2 (or any slot any page just simplifying)<br>
then make a hotkey for slot 1 that has the following lines<br>
<br>
/pause 3<br>
/sit on<br>
/pause 145<br>
/sit off<br>
<br>
----hit 1 then 2 in quick succesion and you will cast the rob and then sit, med and get up in time for it to go off.  I have noticed a slight variation in the timing of the robe, as sometimes when i stand up it goes off automatically, and sometimes it will wait 2 to 3 seconds. It could be lag causing it, im not sure.<br>
<br>
Anyways, there you go lucky robe holders, Props to Thanatopsis for helping me figure it out.<br>
<br>
Supa 56 wiz<br>
Tunare server</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ulikwiteci.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Likwit Eci</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.geocities.com/everquest_02118/button.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>1/9/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>5:44:10 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://www.blizzard.com/images/broodwar/popup/corsair.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: I figured it out</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">well, that makes 28 seconds ok i guess : )</font><P>Likwit Lightninghands..........
